headline.main: U.S. Born Businessman Named as Palermo President
headline.print_headline: U.S. Born Businessman Named as Palermo President

lead_paragraph: U.S. born businessman Paul Baccaglini has been named as the  president of struggling Palermo after he agreed that his fund would take over the struggling Serie A club.
